INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1724, 5, '2013-06-21 12:02:06', '2013-06-21 12:02:06', '[one_half last="no"]\n\n[heading type="h2" margintop="10px" marginbottom="20px" bordered="no" align="center"][color] 1) Investing Is Complicated[/color] [/heading]\n[heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="center"] Today\'s financial markets are overly complex, making it difficult to know which investments are best suited for your specific needs. [/heading]\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[one_half last="yes"]\n\n<a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Complex.png"><img alt="Complex" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Complex.png" width="952" height="604" /></a>\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[separator_full margintop="20px" marginbottom="30px"]\n\n[one_half last="no"]\n\n<a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Cost-Table-no-Total.png"><img alt="" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Cost-Table-no-Total.png" width="634" height="346" /></a>\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[one_half last="yes"]\n\n[heading type="h2" margintop="10px" marginbottom="20px" bordered="no" align="center"][color]2) There Are Too Many Fees[/color] [/heading]\n[heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="center"] Every dollar you pay in fees, is one less dollar you have to reinvest or spend in the future.[/heading]\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="center"] These fees add up and if you aren\'t paying attention... they can cost you anywhere from 3% to 5% in returns a year.* [/heading]\n\n[separator_full margintop="20px" marginbottom="30px"]\n\n[one_half last="no"]\n\n[heading type="h2" margintop="10px" marginbottom="20px" bordered="no" align="center"][color] 3) I Don\'t Have the Time[/color] [/heading]\n[heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="center"] Instead of trying to fit a client into a specific “model” portfolio, we consider each client’s individual needs and create a portfolio based on your own specific risk tolerance and investment goals.[/heading]\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[one_half last="yes"]\n\n<a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Allocation.png"><img alt="Allocation" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Allocation.png" width="752" height="342" /></a>\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[separator_full margintop="20px" marginbottom="30px"]\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Cost-Chart.png"><img class="aligncenter" alt="Cost Chart" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Cost-Chart.png" width="412" height="255" /></a></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n[heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="center"] By leveraging our expertise in technology, Invessence is able to reduce the inefficiencies in our current financial markets and provide a [color] professional &amp; cost-effective [/color] investment plan for any individual, small business or organization.[/heading]\n<div></div>\n&nbsp;', 'The Problem', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'take-a-tour', '', '', '2013-06-21 12:02:06', '2013-06-21 12:02:06', '', 1718, 'http://www.invessence.com/?page_id=1724', 0, 'page', '', 0) ; 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1731, 5, '2013-06-21 12:04:06', '2013-06-21 12:04:06', '[one_half last="no"]\n\n[heading type="h2" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]Our Investing Principles:[/heading]\n\n[accordion id="accordion2"]\n[accordion_child parent="accordion2" title="Diversification" open="no"] [floated float="left" clear="no"][/floated]We avoid taking on too much concentrated risk by investing in a small number of assets and strategies. Our portfolios will be diversified across 4 asset classes (Equity, Bonds, Commodities, Cash) and up to 20 sub-asset classes through different ETFs. [/accordion_child]\n\n[accordion_child parent="accordion2" title="Personalized Plan" open="no"] [floated float="left" clear="no"][/floated]Instead of trying to fit a client into a specific “model” portfolio, we consider each client’s individual needs and create a portfolio based on their own specific risk tolerance and time horizon.[/accordion_child]\n\n[accordion_child parent="accordion2" title="Minimize Cost" open="no"] [floated float="left" clear="no"][/floated]Don\'t chase the hottest or most complicated funds because they generally have the highest fees. The lower your advisory and investment costs, the greater your share of investment returns.[/accordion_child]\n\n[accordion_child parent="accordion2" title="Long Term Investing" open="no"] [floated float="left" clear="no"][/floated]Don\'t try to time the market. It fluctuates over the short-term, focus on investing over the long-term.[/accordion_child]\n\n[accordion_child parent="accordion2" title="Discipline" open="no"] [floated float="left" clear="no"][/floated]You take the time to set-up the right portfolio but don’t do anything to maintain it. Few online brokerages offer free automatic rebalancing but we do! [/accordion_child]\n\n[/accordion][/one_half]\n\n[one_half last="yes"]\n\n<a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Inv-Table.png"><img alt="Inv Table" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Inv-Table.png" width="1337" height="753" /></a>\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[separator_full margintop="20px" marginbottom="30px"]\n\n[heading type="h2" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]Our Methodology:[/heading]\n\n[heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]We create an investment plan and manage a client’s portfolio by seeking to identify the:[/heading]\n\n[heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]\n\n1) Optimal asset classes in which to invest,\n2) Most efficient ETFs to represent each of those asset classes,\n3) Ideal mix of asset classes and ETFs based on the client’s specific risk tolerance, and\n4) Best time to rebalance\n[/heading]\n\n[separator_full margintop="20px" marginbottom="30px"]\n[one_half last="no"]\n[heading type="h2" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]Our Solution:[/heading]\n\n[heading type="h4" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]To tailor our service to each client, Invessence asks each client a series of questions to evaluate both their objective ability and subjective willingness to take risk.\n[/heading]\n\n<a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Questionnaire.png"><img alt="Questionnaire" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Questionnaire.png" width="300" height="214" /></a>\n\n[/one_half]\n[one_half last="yes"]\n\n<a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Asset-Allocation.png"><img alt="Asset Allocation" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Asset-Allocation.png" width="169" height="229" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[heading type="h4" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]Based on your answers, we use our advanced algorithms, to determine an accurate profile of your risk tolerance and construct your optimal portfolio.\n[/heading]\n\n[/one_half]\n[separator_full margintop="20px" marginbottom="30px"]\n[floated float="left" clear="no"][fontawesome icon="laptop" size="extralarge" style="normal" color="dark"][/floated][heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]We bring professional investment management to any individual wanting to create their own investment portfolio, individually tailored to meet your specific risk tolerance and time horizon, at a fraction of the cost of traditional wealth management.[/heading]\n\n[floated float="right" clear="yes"][button size="normal" color="theme" link="#" tooltip=""]Learn More[/button][/floated]', 'Our Solution', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'our-solution', '', '', '2013-06-21 12:04:06', '2013-06-21 12:04:06', '', 1718, 'http://www.invessence.com/?page_id=1731', 0, 'page', '', 0) ; 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1736, 5, '2013-06-21 12:04:41', '2013-06-21 12:04:41', '<p style="text-align: center;">[one_half last="no"]<a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/How-it-works.png"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-2212" alt="How it works" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/How-it-works.png" width="718" height="526" /></a></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n[/one_half]\n\n[one_half last="yes"]\n\n[heading type="h2" margintop="10px" marginbottom="20px" bordered="no" align="left"]It\'s [color]Simple[/color] [/heading]\n\n[floated float="left" clear="no"][fontawesome icon="quote-left" size="extralarge" style="normal" color="dark"][/floated]By opening an account with InvEssence, YOU maintain complete control of YOUR money and how to invest it. Our goal is to provide you with the tools to make the investing process less confusing and more about YOU -- not someone else’s bottom line.\n\n[floated float="right" clear="yes"][button size="normal" color="theme" link="#" tooltip=""]Learn More[/button][/floated]\n\n[/one_half]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[heading type="h4" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"]Step 1: Opening an Account\n\nNew users are required to Register in order to create a username and password. After logging back in, they are directed to enter their personal and financial information needed to create an account.\n\nStep 2: Set Your Investment Goals\n\nAs determined by a questionnaire, each portfolio is constructed to meet the individual’s risk tolerance, time horizon and liquidity needs. The portfolio is designed to serve as a “Core” investment portfolio for medium to long term investing horizons.\n\nStep 3: Create your Portfolio\n\nEach portfolio will allocate across 20 ETFs diversified by asset class (Equity/Bonds/Commodities/Cash), by size (Large/Mid/Small Cap), balancing style (Growth/Value), and geography (Domestic/International/Emerging Markets). The weightings to each asset and investment will change over time as the market fluctuates but Invessence will rebalance the portfolio, on a quarterly basis, so that each asset allocation will always remain balanced.\n\nStep 4: Invest\n\nOnce the investor has confirmed their asset allocation, they will be presented with the actual holdings, weights, and symbols of their portfolio. Upon confirmation, the portfolio will be invested the next business day.\n\nStep 5: Rebalance\n\nOnce you have created a portfolio, Invessence will analyze and rebalance it, because market movements may cause your initial weightings to change. Invessence will automatically rebalance the portfolio to maintain this optimal strategy over time.\n[/heading]\n[heading type="h2" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="center"]NO Middle Man, NO Hidden Costs, NO Confusion[/heading]', 'How it Works', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'how-it-works', '', '', '2013-06-21 12:04:41', '2013-06-21 12:04:41', '', 1718, 'http://www.invessence.com/?page_id=1736', 0, 'page', '', 0) ; 
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1741, 5, '2013-06-21 12:05:32', '2013-06-21 12:05:32', '[heading type="h2" margintop="8px" marginbottom="28px" bordered="no" align="left"][color]Giving Back...[/color][/heading]\n[heading type="h3" margintop="8px" marginbottom="20px" bordered="no" align="left"]Incorporating charitable donations into our business model was one small step that makes a big difference to our investors, and more importantly, to those in need.[/heading]\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Charity-Picture.png"><img class="aligncenter" alt="Charity Picture" src="http://www.invessence.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Charity-Picture.png" width="334" height="218" /></a></p>\n[checklist size="medium"]\n<ul>\n	<li>Our team supports causes that help save and change children’s lives.</li>\n	<li>We are dedicated to making a contribution to charity-based organizations from our company’s profits.</li>\n	<li>Through your investments with Invessence, your financial planning can also incorporate these giving goals.</li>\n</ul>\n[/checklist]', 'Socially Responsible Business', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'socially-responsible-business', '', '', '2013-06-21 12:05:32', '2013-06-21 12:05:32', '', 1718, 'http://www.invessence.com/?page_id=1741', 0, 'page', '', 0) ; 
